Document: Range
Path: godot/classes/class_range.rst
Summary: Describes methods for managing the value and sharing behavior of a Range node.

Method: _value_changed(new_value: float) → void
Called when the Range's value is changed (following the same conditions as value_changed signal).

Method: set_value_no_signal(value: float) → void
Sets the Range's current value to the specified value, without emitting the value_changed signal.

Method: share(with: Node) → void
Binds two Range's together along with any ranges previously grouped with either of them. When any of range's member variables change, it will share the new value with all other ranges in its group.

Method: unshare() → void
Stops the Range from sharing its member variables with any other.